data.description: Come see this gorgeous 3 bedroom, 2 full bath home all on one level! Beautiful original hardwood floors are throughout the house. A gas fireplace is in the living room for those cozy nights. Kitchen has tile floors and all stainless steel appliances. The fenced backyard is perfect for your children or fur babies to run and play. Newer hot water heater, hvac was serviced/fan replaced 2 years ago. This place will not last long.
